<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<style>
body {

  
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
}

html {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

*, *:before, *:after {
  box-sizing: inherit;
}

.column {
  float: left;
  width: 33.3%;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  padding: 0 8px;
}

.card {
  box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  margin: 8px;
}

.about-section {
  padding: 50px;
  text-align: center;
  background-color: #474e5d;
  color: white;
}

.container {
  padding: 0 16px;
}

.container::after, .row::after {
  content: "";
  clear: both;
  display: table;
}

.title {
  color: grey;
}

.button {
  border: none;
  outline: 0;
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 8px;
  color: white;
  background-color: #000;
  text-align: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  width: 100%;
}

.button:hover {
  background-color: #555;
}

@media screen and (max-width: 650px) {
  .column {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="about-section">
  <h1>About Us</h1>
  <h5>Meni's - the leading chain of flower and gift stores in Israel, provides its customers with a unique and convenient shopping experience, while maintaining service and courtesy.
    At the chain's branches, we make sure that you create the freshest flowers, in innovative designs, as well as the wine packages,
    Gift and pampering packages, birth gifts and a wide range of original and heart-warming gifts.
    The flowers of Meni's are selected one by one and harvested from fields and warmed in the country, while maintaining their quality and size, taking into account the seasons and Israeli buckwheat.
  </h5>
  <p>Resize the browser window to see that this page is responsive by the way.</p>
</div>

<h2 style="text-align:center">Our Team</h2>
<div class="row">
  <div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/trump.jpg" alt="Jane" style="width:100%">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Donald Trump</h2>
        <p class="title">CEO & Founder</p>
        <p>Donald John Trump (born June 14, 1946).</p>
        <p>trump1@example.com</p>
        <p><button class="button">Contact</button></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/bibi.jpg" alt="Mike" style="width:100%">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Benjamin Netanyahu</h2>
        <p class="title">Art Director</p>
        <p>Benjamin Netanyahu Prime Minister of Israel.</p>
        <p>Netanyahu@example.com</p>
        <p><button class="button">Contact</button></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="column">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/bayden2.jpg" alt="John" style="width:100%">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Joe Biden</h2>
        <p class="title">Designer</p>
        <p>Joseph Robinette Biden Jr.</p>
        <p>Biden@example.com</p>
        <p><button class="button">Contact</button></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
